content:
Users can give feedback on Copilot responses by hovering over a response and selecting a thumbs up or thumbs down. They can also select a reason why the response was unhelpful. In the mobile app, users can long-press a system-generated response to provide feedback.

This change applies to Lightning Experience, Salesforce mobile apps for iOS and Android, Field Service mobile apps for iOS and Android, and Sales Cloud Everywhere in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions with Einstein add-ons. Setup is available on the desktop site.

The feature is available the week of July 1, 2024, on iOS and Android devices.
title: Give Feedback on Copilot Responses
